nhc_headline: ...HUMBERTO EXPECTED TO BRING TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS TO BERMUDA ON TUESDAY... ...DANGEROUS SURF WILL AFFECT BERMUDA AND MOST OF THE U.S. EAST COAST THIS WEEK...
summary: ...HUMBERTO EXPECTED TO BRING TROPICAL STORM CONDITIONS TO BERMUDA ON TUESDAY... ...DANGEROUS SURF WILL AFFECT BERMUDA AND MOST OF THE U.S. EAST COAST THIS WEEK... As of 5:00 PM AST Sun Sep 28 the center of Humberto was located near 25.5, -65.4 with movement NW at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 937 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 145 mph.
